  "detailed_description": "<h1>Mistery Free Pass</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/585d75d668e654f6c0bb35866303c14f.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Free Pass will be permanently available on Steam with unlimited number of matches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While in-game store, battle passes and other external content are locked, the core gameplay is identical to the full version. You can match with all players as usual, and achievements will carry over after purchasing the full version.</p></p><br><h1>FREE DELUXE DLC</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/27ca8eb5f26fec3531e0194fb9d82441.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everyone who buys MISTERY gets FREE DELUXE DLC, which is automatically added to the library. It includes an epic skin, title, and 500 coins.</p></p><br><h1>Join Us</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/fa495039aae401ba7dd290291dc33c48.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our community to chat and team up with more friends. The link is on the right-column of the page.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Containment Breach has occurred around the site, bringing a heavy mist. Behind it, monsters are stirring. Among the people, betrayal is spreading.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to MISTERY, a multiplayer game about cooperating, crafting, surviving, and escaping. Or, it is more about pretending, deceiving, sabotaging, and murdering!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improved upon features in similar games like Dread Hunger and Project Winter, MISTERY offers enhanced gameplay, storytelling, and friendship-destroying experiences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/d10eb8df9332eb30998f8feaa88b9f3d.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to 9 players cooperate and explore the crumbling site. During the day, scavenge resources, craft weapons, and retrieve batteries. At night, use batteries to charge the lamp, and survive the long dark by employing items and skills to repel waves of monsters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/d609281575ba7d22afabb59c887d638e.poster.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/d609281575ba7d22afabb59c887d638e.webm?t=1753931289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/d609281575ba7d22afabb59c887d638e.mp4?t=1753931289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/20027b5d9d5549a25e1ed18ef38f2f28.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware, someone among the survivors has been contaminated into beasts wearing human skin. Or worse: they are the anomalies imprisoned in the site, eager to rip reality apart! Don't expose your back to anyone. If you notice someone behaving weirdly, let your allies know immediately - if there's anyone left to trust! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/33a6322e7e3ab9b914b814dd0ee49727.poster.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/33a6322e7e3ab9b914b814dd0ee49727.webm?t=1753931289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/33a6322e7e3ab9b914b814dd0ee49727.mp4?t=1753931289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/d0c890167d88f841a09d92e4a1396935.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play 10+ unique heroes as you want. Each of them has the potential to change the game - Gunner uses his heavy fire, Engineer finds batteries quickly, Doctor heals others, Spy hides in the darkness...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/ce595a402f8cce550fb30de19a33123c.poster.avif?t=1753931289\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/ce595a402f8cce550fb30de19a33123c.webm?t=1753931289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/ce595a402f8cce550fb30de19a33123c.mp4?t=1753931289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/6f6589b4c59283312596c3361de09743.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Despite the site being on the brink of collapse, some facilities are still functional. Watch others through the monitor, recover resources from locked safeboxes, or trigger electric traps to catch unarmed victims! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/382745a0f5a14c56bd9ed6991064c6e1.poster.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/382745a0f5a14c56bd9ed6991064c6e1.webm?t=1753931289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/382745a0f5a14c56bd9ed6991064c6e1.mp4?t=1753931289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/0f6dc0029a6164d15622c49ef3ff40ce.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arm yourself! Hoard bullets, medicines, and enhancers. Craft powerful weapons, get unique equipment from airdrop boxes, and unlock mutation powers! Use your wits and reflexes in the deadliest fights to carve a bloody path out of chaos! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/4cc232689d98643abdffd730e51b25c6.poster.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/4cc232689d98643abdffd730e51b25c6.webm?t=1753931289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/4cc232689d98643abdffd730e51b25c6.mp4?t=1753931289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/a78657f6c120edf5ae3f8a02d25e64f8.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By introducing a lot of random encounter events, the game builds an environmental storytelling mechanism of new-weird tales. Check them to uncover the true secrets behind Mistery. In the future, new stories will be released with new mechanics, anomalies, characters, maps, and more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/4a4351f12840eaebb6d81d09693f0f5e.poster.avif?t=1753931289\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/4a4351f12840eaebb6d81d09693f0f5e.webm?t=1753931289\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537010/extras/4a4351f12840eaebb6d81d09693f0f5e.mp4?t=1753931289\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
